ell as the first search for\nthird-generation leptoquarks in the final state with a pair of hadronically\ndecaying tau leptons and jets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Dec 2016 21:49:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Mar 2017 18:12:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-21"}
