 p-p\noperations, including runs at 40 MHz bunch rate, Pb-Pb operations and p-Pb\noperations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2016 03:39:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
