r from 1978 in the sense\nthat to some arguments given there not in a detailed manner, we give here for\nall of these complete proofs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2016 11:03:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-06"}
